      "content": "That makes sense. I'll look into the unit of measure and the scanner sync. Regarding the last point about theft or loss—since these are tiny components like resistors and capacitors, it's hard to imagine anyone just walking out with them unnoticed. Is there anything else that usually accounts for \"unexplained\" loss that isn't just outright theft?",
